    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied it since day one, kept it strictly in the garage, and it\u2019s honestly as close to perfect as you can get. It\u2019s been impeccably maintained and is ready for its next adventure. I'm looking for a smooth, easy sale, so feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
      "price": 43500.0,
