      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving precision. The S54 inline-six features a fully addressed VANOS system and shimmed valves, delivering seamless power through the Getrag 6-speed manual. The rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the drivetrain is anchored by a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry is factory-spec with fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the communicative steering and lateral grip remain uncompromised. This is a collector-grade machine with zero mechanical debt.",
      "price": 46500.0,
